short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Docbot plugin for integration with Docbot Slack integration.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Docbot is a Chrome extension that allows team members to easily aggregate custom content by easily saving a URL that is analyzed and categorized by the Watson Alchemy natural language processing algorithm and URL's are easily searchable by relevancy for target words via a simple Slack command integration.

Share resources that YOUR team has found value in for what you do.

BETA: Individual team registration not currently available.
